Package: TargomoR
Type: Package
Title: An R Interface to the Targomo API
Version: 0.1.1.9003
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Mason-Thom", email = "chrismasonthom@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package allows R users to exploit the Targomo REST API. Currently it 
    supports the Polygon, Routing and Time services, as well as access to Targomo basemaps.
    The MultiGraph service is not supported.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://cwthom.github.io/TargomoR
BugReports: https://github.com/cwthom/TargomoR/issues
